items.badge_description: Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 5 different venues categories as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 2!
It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 160 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 33!

items.checkin_comment: Earlier today. Almost clear golden. Malty, bready, hoppy and quite dry with good bitterness. A welcoming beer in the sun.

user.bio: Gonna wear them happy shoes tonight!

items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 100 check-ins with a photo.

Grab your stein and dawn your lederhosen because it’s time to trek through the mountains of one of the world's most historic beer regions. That's 5 different beers from a brewery located in Austria. Try 5 more for Level 2!

items.checkin_comment: På rekommendation av kyparen; bättre än förväntat! En aning bett, trots ganska svag, och fylligare än klassisk inhemsk lager. Helt ok!
